# AWS Amplify Redirects for Bellavista Nursing Homes
# Forces HTTPS and WWW for optimal SEO ranking

# Redirect non-WWW to WWW (HTTPS)
https://bellavistanursinghomes.com/* https://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/:splat 301

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS + WWW
http://bellavistanursinghomes.com/* https://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/:splat 301

# Redirect HTTP WWW to HTTPS WWW
http://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/* https://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/:splat 301

# Redirect root paths
https://bellavistanursinghomes.com/ https://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/ 301
http://bellavistanursinghomes.com/ https://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/ 301
http://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/ https://www.bellavistanursinghomes.com/ 301